Im going to college to get my books. Holy shit they're expensive fucking books.  God i have a feeling college is going to be so tough.

WoW, it feels like i haven't written here in so long. well, i have written every now and then but they've been here and there comments, nothing specific about me or my life.

i started my new job at the DOLLAR CASTLE lol...its so boring, im a cashier and all i do is ring up shit to people. but im on my feet the whole day so i get so tired, and drained out. like how i feel right now. I just cleaned the dirty shit in my house, and im even more tired than i was coming home from a  10 hour shift today.  I love working those hours though because it's so much more worth it to go there and stay there for a long time, as opposed to going for 5 hours. UgH i hate 5 hour shifts.

So, joey and i are great. hes so amazing. sometimes i get pissed off at him, just to get pissed off at him, and i blow things out of proportion just because i want to break the glass you know? like, hes too perfect, there must be some faults, some mistakes. but he hasnt failed yet. he treats me like a princess, i can tell from the look in his eyes, he absolutely adores me. awww my pumpkin. today, we went to the pet store so he could buy Oreo a cage, for the winter, and such. it was sooo cute i saw these kitties and i wanted them alll of them! =[ they were little babies omg sooo pretty but they were taken care of already, they had that surgery so they cant have babies omg i felt so bad for them, they couldnt even choose if they wanted to have kids or not =[ and thats the whole point for me to even have a girl dog or cat....so it can breed. i think ashley is right, i want puppies sooooo bad because i cant have my own babies yet =[

im so nervous for college, i dont know why. i know i can do good if i dont know anyone...and sometiems i can do even better if i know someone.... because of the competition. but who knows? im taking introduction to logic (philosophy), introduction to psychology, math(intermediate algebra), and english (composition 1). those are tough fucking classes, 13 hrs total for the semester, i cant BELIEVE im taking PHILOSOPHY and PSYCHOLOGY together!  someone pray for me!

so far, so good.....but im really tired. i gotta open up tomorrow!

i cant wait to get my laptop. im so excited, seriously. 3 more weeks!!!!! i think im gonna get it from sam's club, because they have really good policies on returns/exchanges. i can return it up to 6 months after i get it, if something is wrong or i dont like it. im gonna get the best one just beacuse. lol

anyways im tired as fuck its 1 in the morning i gotta wake up at 9 so that isn't cool. goodnight.

i miss my cousin, Ayad. i used to write in my journal, entitled 'ayad'. i feel horrible that i havent visited his grave in so long. r.i.p. i love you cousin.

so, today is my first day writing in here. thanks to my gurl ashley who set up all this and convinced me to write in a livejournal! she even set up my pics! ash ur so hot lol.......
so today was pretty gay. normal day. i didnt see joey today becausee i went to my dads house and he went to work =/  sometimes i wonder how i got such a great guy and what made me go from robert to him...
i still miss robert sometimes, what can i say 2 years of a fucking waste
i miss the way he kissed me or rubbed on my back, the way he cracks a joke when im trying to be serious and always makes me smile because hed be so cute, the cute notes he threw to me saying i love you, the cds he made me, the flowers and candies he got me and my mom on v-day......but i regret being with him those four days. its like the devil was in him and took the love out of my heart. i got this amazing guy and im not appreciative of it. pathetic. why do i still miss rob? is something wrong with my brain?....maybe i got so used to him for so long and its gonna take me time to get used to a guy that treats me like a princess and not an asshole 3/4 the time

not to mention, joey is SOOOOO CUTE! =] =] =]

 

so did i mention that i have the bestest friend in the whole entire world named lorrin ! i wav my lorrikinz even tho this summer i barely got to see her but seriously shes such a good friend, a good listener, compromiser and compassionate person. she understands everything and tries her hardest to make ppl happy! i missed her so much when she was in florida this weekend goddamn you for leaving me! thats ourour picture together at club bleu omg we always have a blast together isnt she stunning!

im out. peace love happiness

Amelia
